{"tid":2347584,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"62歲性感阿婆硬撼深田恭子，宮崎美子成目標隨時爆黃昏戀","createTime":"2020-12-31T07:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T12:48:41.000Z","uid":38539,"like":12,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"00241f18f6fc2e9670b2fb3d6ffbfc691d133a51","tid":2347584,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/veSwrRS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FveSwrRS.png&h=c01f2a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年屆62歲的日本女星宮崎美子，最近為紀念入行40周年，推出性感月曆及純影集，以比堅尼泳裝上陣，由攝影大師篠山紀信操刀，令她成為話題人物，宮崎獲讚身材白滑，吸引力更被外界拿來與性感女神深田恭子相比，爭做今年的月曆女王。<br />\n<br />\n宮崎美子以性感阿婆形象刺激人氣，威到獲NHK電視台邀請為今晚舉行的《紅白歌唱大賽》擔任評判，最近她出席活動時還變風頭躉，與一班扮成《鬼滅之刃》角色的粉絲在無限列車合照留念。目前單身的宮崎美子，正成為傳媒的新目標，除到掌握到她的住址外，更打算揭露她的私生活，不排除將會有戀情曝光。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201231/DYN7PKMP2VCPBO34HUEC5MYWSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201231%2FDYN7PKMP2VCPBO34HUEC5MYWSM%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=b949c6a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201231%2FDYN7PKMP2VCPBO34HUEC5MYWSM%2F&h=1d4dc855\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201231/DYN7PKMP2VCPBO34HUEC5MYWSM/</a>"},{"pid":"3e33e70f11559c538e6f7c76f1310f46548b44f0","tid":2347584,"uid":344464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:13:03.000Z","msg":"屌咩"},{"pid":"f741bc6cf3047d5d8275bdc791593be9c21af968","tid":2347584,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"62.............."},{"pid":"d489b5ec1389e076d29da0a4aa06bf2fc99c5fd4","tid":2347584,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"還曆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bada4d16044402550fe247ce79e8fa9dc7a15456",